</style><p>白銀ノエルさんは9月1日、9月13日までの配信活動休止を発表されております。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/shiroganenoel/status/1697444163716100570?t=9j-Q3ATfHGdey0MNilO1Uw&amp;s=19</div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCdyqAaZDKHXg4Ahi7VENThQ" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Noel Ch. 白銀ノエル</a>／<a href="https://twitter.com/shiroganenoel">白銀ノエル<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2694.png" alt="⚔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />ホロライブ3期生</a>／ <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/talents/shirogane-noel/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">白銀ノエル</a></p><cite>YouTube / X (Twitter) / ホロライブプロダクション</cite></blockquote><p>( <em>P2y.jp 管理代表者「2号さん (仮)」</em> ／バーチャル・メタバース・VTuber情報) </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="NmU9hWiomJ"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-encountered-a-problem-logging-in-to-her-official-x-twitter-account/">VTuber Shiragane Noel Encountered a Problem Logging in to her Official X (Twitter) Account</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber Shiragane Noel Encountered a Problem Logging in to her Official X (Twitter) Account&#8221; &#8212; P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-encountered-a-problem-logging-in-to-her-official-x-twitter-account/embed/#?secret=8dCsxIyyKL#?secret=NmU9hWiomJ" data-secret="NmU9hWiomJ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> The post <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-encountered-a-problem-logging-in-to-her-official-x-twitter-account/">VTuber 白銀ノエル X (Twitter) 公式アカウントにログイン出来ない不具合が発生</a>first appeared on <a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> .; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-encountered-a-problem-logging-in-to-her-official-x-twitter-account/feed/ 0 100558
